platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: With 70 million monthly readers, Wattpad forms a communal experience around the love of writing. Offering words to new readers and a platform to writers, Wattpad creates a kinship between authors and their fans that has never been more intimate.
A communal experience around the love of writing. Offering words to new readers and a platform to writers, theres a strong kinship here between authors and their fans.
